{The bidding has been as shown.   

You have a perfect hand for a Takeout Double. Singleton in their suit, 4-card support for the other three suits and 13 HCP. You Double. Partner responds 1\H. What do you say next? 

Yes, you like the \Hs. But remember, you forced partner to bid and his response showed 8 or fewer points. You are not strong enough to consider a game so you pass.}

